xorg-server
------------------------------------------
X.Org servers

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.0-50
  libfontenc1-1.0.4-10
  libfreetype6-2.3.9-1
  libgcc1-4.3.2-2
  libGL1-7.4.4-1
  libpixman1_0-0.14.0-10
  libX11_6-1.2.1-1
  libXau6-1.0.4-10
  libXdmcp6-1.0.2-10
  libXext6-1.0.5-10
  openssl-0.9.8k-2
  xauth-1.0.3-1
  xcursor-themes-1.0.1-1
  xkbcomp-1.0.5-1
  xkeyboard-config-1.4-1
  zlib0-1.2.3-10

